'''弗朗西斯科·西奧尼爾·何塞'''（Francisco Sionil José，{{bd|1924年|12月3日|2022年|1月6日|catIdx=José}}<ref>{{Cite news|date=2022-01-06|title=National Artist F Sionil Jose dies at 97|url=https://www.rappler.com/life-and-style/literature/national-artist-f-sionil-jose-dies/|access-date=2022-01-06|work=Rappler|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220106164814/https://www.rappler.com/life-and-style/literature/national-artist-f-sionil-jose-dies/}}</ref>
），通常署名為'''F.西奧尼爾·何塞'''（F. Sionil José），菲律賓華文報刊譯為'''尚尼·扶西'''<ref name="#1">[http://worldnews.net.ph/post/5422 老烏鴉的叫聲] {{Wayback|url=http://worldnews.net.ph/post/5422 |date=20160310181038 }}菲律濱世界日報2014-04-04</ref>，是[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]最被广泛阅读的英语作家之一。他的小说描绘了阶级斗争的社会基础以及菲律宾的殖民主义。何塞的作品已被翻译成22种语言，包括[[朝鲜语|朝鲜语]]、[[印度尼西亚语|印度尼西亚语]]、[[俄语|俄语]]、[[拉脱维亚语|拉脱维亚语]]、[[乌克兰语|乌克兰语]]和[[荷兰语|荷兰语]]。<ref name=BBC>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/3109471.stm Jose, F. Sionil. Sense of the City: Manila, BBC News, BBC.co.uk, July 30, 2003] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/asia-pacific/3109471.stm |date=20071002133824 }}, retrieved on June 14, 2007</ref><ref name=RandomHouse>[http://www.randomhouse.com/author/results.pperl?authorid=14838 Author Spotlight: F. Sionil Jose, Random House, RandomHouse.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.randomhouse.com/author/results.pperl?authorid=14838 |date=20080225090702 }}, retrieved on June 14, 2007</ref><ref name=Inquirer>[http://globalnation.inquirer.net/features/features/view_article.php?article_id=62431 Macansantos, Priscilla Supnet.  A Hometown as Literature for F. Sionil José, Global Nation/Features, Inquirer, Inquirer.net] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716082346/http://globalnation.inquirer.net/features/features/view_article.php?article_id=62431 |date=2011-07-16 }}, April 25, 2007, retrieved on: June 14, 2007</ref><ref name=Jrank>[http://biography.jrank.org/pages/4741/Sionil-Jose-F-rancisco.html Yabes, Leopoldo Y. and Judson Knight, Francisco Sionil Jose Biography, Contemporary Novelists, Volume 16, Jrank.org] {{Wayback|url=http://biography.jrank.org/pages/4741/Sionil-Jose-F-rancisco.html |date=20110906143517 }}, retrieved on June 16, 2007</ref><ref name=TKT>[http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/art_view.asp?newsIdx=1921&categoryCode=142 Garcia, Cathy Rose. “Author F. Sionil Jose’s Insight on Philippines” (an article about F. Sionil Jose’s novel, Ermita – published in Korean)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/art/art_view.asp?newsIdx=1921&categoryCode=142 |date=20110520103323 }}, Arts & Living, The Korea Times, KoreaTimes.co.kr, April 27, 2007</ref><ref name=BAorg>[http://bookasia.org/bbs/view.php?id=news&no=86 Garcia, Cathy Rose. “Author F. Sionil Jose’s Insight on Philippines” (an article about F. Sionil Jose’s novel: Ermita – published in Korean)] {{Wayback|url=http://bookasia.org/bbs/view.php?id=news&no=86 |date=20111003194218 }}, BookAsia.org (Korean website), April 27, 2007</ref>

